Token Budget Visualization. Horizontal bar: Context Window (128k tokens). Segments: System Prompt (2k, blue), RAG Context (20k, green), Chat History (10k, yellow), User Query (1k, red), Output Reserve (4k, purple), Safety Buffer (remaining, gray). Overlapping blocks showing Chunking: 512 tokens with 64 overlap. Truncation strategies: First-N, Last-N, Middle, Summary. Infographic style, German labels.